    "- `msno.matrix()` visualizes a missingness matrix\n",
    "- `msno.bar()` visualizes a missngness barplot\n",
    "- `msno.dendrogram()` visualizes all connections (clusters) between NA's\n",
    "- `plt.show()` to show the plot"
   ]
